These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, rowing, parkour
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##8
3. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Sport   | parkour | rowing | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, board-games, camping
1. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##8
2. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | photography | camping | board-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, milk, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Beverage   | milk | water | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-4::.
